# Advanced GitHub Actions Notes

needs
Defines job dependencies.

strategy.matrix
Runs a job with multiple configurations.

workflow_dispatch
Allows manual workflow execution.

schedule
Runs workflows automatically using cron.

artifact
Stores files produced by a workflow.

upload-artifact
Uploads files.

download-artifact
Downloads files.

GITHUB_OUTPUT
Passes outputs between steps.

environment
Defines deployment environments.
